{"tid":1281683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【所有曾被抄牌既戰友入黎】","createTime":"2019-07-03T10:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T11:27:06.000Z","uid":100930,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5ac1d19bb67d11939ad005a51f7ba0b06d144fa2","tid":1281683,"uid":100930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:53:07.000Z","msg":"心理戰<br />\n由尋日到宜家 不斷有白色恐怖<br />\n我明白大家驚同擔心 <br />\n但其實有幾樣野大家要諗清楚<br />\n<br />\n第一：大掃除<br />\n控告一個人 必須要有證據 才能控告<br />\n所以得閒既話 呢幾日執下屋<br />\n電話 電腦老化咪換左佢<br />\nD衫褲鞋襪殘左咪dump<br />\n假如d野好重要既話 交比你信任既人 佢地保管住先<br />\n<br />\n第二：了解所有有關法例既野<br />\n上網有好多懶人包<br />\n有咩事記得打電話比律師先<br />\n保障自己權利 乜9都唔好講<br />\nD狗大部分鐘意用法例嚇9大家<br />\n所以 增強database 睇多d<br />\n幫到自己 可以幫到其他人<br />\n<br />\n第三 調整心態<br />\n你做左以上兩樣野<br />\n已經好撚累<br />\n宜家去沖個靚涼<br />\n睇下on9片 <br />\n令自己心情輕鬆先<br />\n然後！！同自己講 我無做錯野 亦唔需要驚<br />\n因為你後面有好多人撐緊你<br />\n個信念一定要夠堅定 個人先可以冷靜<br />\n我知有好多人都唔敢講自己有參與<br />\n唯有搵d有出去野餐既人<br />\n互相扶持<br />\n<br />\n最後 自殺解決唔到問題<br />\n政府連200萬人都唔撚理<br />\n何況一條人命？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 9/6 358<br />\n歡迎大家pm我<br />\n一齊互相交流 互相扶持乜都好"},{"pid":"9b2a3bcb39d89fa32efa7980b2ef2b15849c290a","tid":1281683,"uid":100930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:53:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abc961f368234bac0e5b6cac9fa581b3b3afddef","tid":1281683,"uid":199024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:54:03.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"608a070b34917ab79917172f3d0c147e14bed248","tid":1281683,"uid":260715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:54:50.000Z","msg":"&lt;警民關係呀&gt; 1823舉報+查詢進度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1281633\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1281633</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c39f0487e1da12aa0c8b4048febbde686f598a0b","tid":1281683,"uid":100930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:55:54.000Z","msg":"香港人頂撚住"},{"pid":"5e292a1da258f632bed06169357dc06247482e59","tid":1281683,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efc39d5c1095b33e3d1747c172b2fd7a7810b175","tid":1281683,"uid":100930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7968f95c43d84b552d412f6d8ae7ebd8347d031a","tid":1281683,"uid":100930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:10:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"811446a22a360dc125104ee880c37e7f63e4c0be","tid":1281683,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:13:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d6c54275916741fffc0f33b55df08fc03fcab405","tid":1281683,"uid":268801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:14:04.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"6bcb1b85c558043e0c6e9d005e9d6729abfe46cd","tid":1281683,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:14:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6c13f58b4e0b5dda1c21f382e49a63c18c55303","tid":1281683,"uid":262507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:14:43.000Z","msg":"班狗開始做野，大家去過野餐記得抹嘴，野餐後須知<br />\n🔻🔻🔻🔻🔻🔻🔻🔻🔻🔻🔻<br />\n(1) 喺公眾地方唔好透露曾到現場，包括學校 / 餐廳 / 街，亦唔好放上連登 / fb / ig。如果一定要透露，你淨係去咗維園71遊行，行到中環遮打道就返咗屋企<br />\n<br />\n(2) 輕傷自行處理，要睇醫生切密透露原因同地方，自己作個故仔 (例如屋企整親)，遇狗查問千祈唔好緊張，最緊要平常心唔好敵視狗隻，講返你作嘅故仔內容就可以<br />\n<br />\n(3) 棄晒所有夢境出現過嘅衣物 (衫 / 鞋 / 袋 / 袋 / 眼鏡 / 手錶)&nbsp;以及任何裝備 (頭盔 / 豬嘴 / 手套)&nbsp;，如果貴 / 唔捨得，可暫時寄存可信任又唔關事嘅親戚朋友<br />\n<br />\n(4) 要棄裝就盡量拆件，去遠少少同多幾個地方分散棄<br />\n<br />\n(5)&nbsp;剪髮、染髮、改變髮型<br />\n<br />\n(6)&nbsp;唔好立即更換八達通，之前已經試過即換法官會懷疑，交畀朋友叫佢幫你呢幾日繼續用，之後就可以整唔見，記得唔好退飛<br />\n<br />\n(7)&nbsp;刪除一切現場影嘅相，因為唔係你開部電話撳delete就完全刪除，唔熟IT嘅人，最簡單多次format成部機<br />\n<br />\n(8) 電話長期set密碼，disable faceid 同 touchid<br />\n<br />\n(9) 電話clear所有相關嘅tg whatsapp內容，del tg account，清google location history，檢查一切有可能透露你位置嘅settings<br />\n<br />\n(10)&nbsp;facebook / ig 改私隱設定，所有私人相同post要set返private / friends only，唔好俾狗認樣。刪哂所有明確地同自己立場唔同既人（驚有人報串）<br />\n<br />\n(11) 曾進入建築物者，trade電話，用咸水處理電子產品<br />\n<br />\n(12a) 曾經直接進攻者，你哋有機會係最先被狗咬嘅一群，清理屋企一切可疑物&nbsp;(包括任何關政治事嘅嘢，e.g. 反送中傳單、天琦助選Tee、民族論)<br />\n<br />\n(12b) (續)&nbsp;換電腦harddisk並安裝windows同其他軟件 (目的係你屋企要有一部正常運作而清白嘅機)，唔好有電腦枱冇電腦 / 有電腦冇windows，舊harddisk交可信任朋友保管，唔熟手嘅搵IT朋友幫，再唔係成部電腦換<br />\n<br />\n(12c) (續) 如harddisk要棄，搵水浸、𠝹刀盡量劃花、消磁、槌仔打到佢變形<br />\n<br />\n(13) 如被咬，我無嘢講，我要見律師，小心扮友善狗隻扮傾計套料，全部狗都係狗<br />\n<br />\n(14) 冇律師陪同下唔可以簽嘢，一簽咗就輸<br />\n<br />\n(15) 協助調查可拒絕，冇搜查令唔使開門，但如果有法律文件必須合作，搜查令睇清楚可搜查地方同物件，另外可以要求律師在場先搜。協助調查唔係要即刻。例如呢幾日你肚瀉唔得 同女分手心情唔好。<br />\n<br />\n(16) 隨身攜帶被捕律師電話，唔好諗住save係電話就算，因為如果真係被捕佢地第一目標一定係電話<br />\n<br />\n🔺🔺🔺🔺🔺🔺🔺🔺🔺🔺🔺🔺<br />\n野餐後須知 一 定 要 睇⬆️"},{"pid":"df79f19572568ca3c8eed90b683f5f815daf3198","tid":1281683,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:15:11.000Z","msg":"如果警察證明到我去過立法會，係咪就會坐監？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1280593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1280593</a>"},{"pid":"65f1a185b98949517978443e4fd07c94cd8a1e68","tid":1281683,"uid":36411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf0141dd6d2404fc717ce3292fa75db3bc04b30","tid":1281683,"uid":100930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65f1a185b98949517978443e4fd07c94cd8a1e68","tid":1281683,"uid":36411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5ca95f4a4b7ca7f6852efe3127fa9400e74a77","tid":1281683,"uid":100930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:27:06.000Z","msg":"推 調整心態！"}]}